     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================


			    Test44
                            ------
                     Author A.Bagulya
             
The test is based on HADR01 example.
The purpose of this test is to validate Bragg peak distribution.
The results of simulation ASCII file is created. The macro
files for proton, He4 and C12 are prepared. Different electromagnetic Physics
Lists are available.

How to run it:
1) compilation
unsetenv $G4ANALYSIS_USE
setenv G4ANALYSIS_USE_ROOT 1
gmake
cd utils
gmake
2) unsetenv REFERENCE (optional)
source run.csh 9.3p01

